ppaurl
======

ppaurl is a utility to add PPA repositories to the system

Download
--------

Download the [package][dlp] *or* checkout the source:

    $ git clone https://github.com/atareao/ppaurl


Installation
------------

    $ sudo add-apt-repositoy ppa:atareao/ppaurl
    $ sudo apt-get update
    $ sudo apt-get install ppaurl
